snippet.title: Super Mario 64 Plus - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Mario 64 Plus is a fork of the Super Mario 64 PC Port that focuses on customizability and aims to add features that not only fix some of the issues found in the base game but also enhance the gameplay overall with extra options.

Download: https://www.mfgg.net/?act=resdb&param=02&c=2&id=38190

My Twitter: https://twitter.com/MorsGames

Logo made by Benial: https://twitter.com/Benial17
